snippet.title: Prehistoric Tales
snippet.description:
Bring an ancient world to vibrant life as you build and protect a fledgling settlement! 

Raise small cities out of the ground, fend off fierce dinosaurs and spend hours enjoying exciting gameplay. As you tend to your budding civilization, be sure to manage your resources well so you can feed and house the villagers. Exciting missions will appear on the screen, are you up for the challenge?

Take the first steps on an epic journey to greatness today!

• Complete thrilling missions
• Unlock bonuses and earn achievements!
• Build a vibrant world
• Overcome fierce enemies
